emented (story 10-2)');\n    50→  }\n    51→\n    52→  getBuildCommands(): string[] {\n    53→    throw new Error('NodejsProvider.getBuildCommands not yet implemented (story 10-2)');\n    54→  }\n    55→\n    56→  getTestCommands(): string[] {\n    57→    throw new Error('NodejsProvider.getTestCommands not yet implemented (story 10-2)');\n    58→  }\n    59→\n    60→  getSemgrepLanguages(): string[] {\n    61→    throw new Error('NodejsProvider.getSemgrepLanguages not yet implemented (story 10-2)');\n    62→  }\n    63→\n    64→  parseTestOutput(_output: string): TestCounts {\n    65→    throw new Error('NodejsProvider.parseTestOutput not yet implemented (story 10-2)');\n    66→  }\n    67→\n    68→  parseCoverageReport(_dir: string): number {\n    69→    throw new Error('NodejsProvider.parseCoverageReport not yet implemented (story 10-2)');\n    70→  }\n    71→\n    72→  getProjectName(_dir: string): string | null {\n    73→    throw new Error('NodejsProvider.getProjectName not yet implemented (story 10-2)');\n    74→  }\n    75→}\n    76→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_014osh4xMtXKp3eoJrCF5J4g","session_id":"ec2bf7d9-1cd3-4665-9804-65790a3eadb3","uuid":"c0a13b89-d879-4f56-a757-25ab97a1b214","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:57:03.781Z"}
